      <groundspeak:short_description html="True">&lt;b&gt;17 April 2027, 09:00 - 16:00&lt;/b&gt;</groundspeak:short_description>
      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MOGA 2027 – Midwest Open Geocaching Adventure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Get ready for a full day of geocaching fun, friendly competition, and community at &lt;strong&gt;MOGA 2027!&lt;/strong&gt; Whether you&amp;#39;re a seasoned cacher or just getting started, this event offers something for everyone.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;📅 Date:&lt;/strong&gt; April 17, 2027&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;📍 Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Norfolk, Nebrsaka&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;🕘 Main Event Hours:&lt;/strong&gt; 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;🏆 Awards Ceremony:&lt;/strong&gt; 7:00 PM – 8:30 PM&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;🎯 What to Expect&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🧭 Competitive Events&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Put your skills to the test in a variety of competitions throughout the day, including:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Puzzle-solving competition&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Individual competition&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;2 person team competition&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;4 person team competition&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Additional geocaching challenges (details announced closer to the event)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🎉 Side Activities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Looking for something more relaxed? Join in on:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Poker Run&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Cribbage Run&lt;br /&gt;
	These fun activities are perfect for all experience levels and add an extra layer of adventure to your day.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🛍️ Vendors &amp;amp; Shopping&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Browse geocaching gear and collectibles from vendors offering a variety of swag. Don’t forget to stop by the &lt;strong&gt;MOGA Central Store&lt;/strong&gt; for exclusive event items!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;🏅 Awards Ceremony&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Wrap up the day by celebrating participants and winners during the awards ceremony from &lt;strong&gt;7:00 PM to 8:30 PM&lt;/strong&gt;. It’s a great time to connect, share stories, and recognize achievements from the day.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;📌 Additional Notes&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;More details on competitions, rules, and specific venues in and around Norfolk will be provided as the event approaches.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Be sure to bring your gear, a sense of adventure, and plenty of energy!&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;There will be a Friday night welcome event and Sunday events to be published later.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We hope to see you at &lt;strong&gt;MOGA 2027&lt;/strong&gt; in Norfolk for an unforgettable day of geocaching excitement!&lt;/p&gt;
</groundspeak:long_description>
