          <groundspeak:type>Attended</groundspeak:type>
          <groundspeak:finder id="3364503">BadDogRanch</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">Thank you for all the fun you provide.  We so enjoy coming down to this park and attending the event.  We have gotten to meet so many wonderful people over the years and look forward to coming here</groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
        <groundspeak:log id="1369046055">
          <groundspeak:date>2026-06-27T21:17:38Z</groundspeak:date>
          <groundspeak:type>Attended</groundspeak:type>
          <groundspeak:finder id="1800547">BlueRah</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">Another great day of geocaching with like minded folks. And, as usual, plenty of great caches, and food. Thanks to Gary, Liz and the Park staff for all they do to make this happen. 
Cheers </groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
        <groundspeak:log id="1369038281">
